node.text:
Day 22 of Circuit Breaker.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Nosh Kitchen has recently partnered with the Health Promotion Board to come up with healthy bentos and beverages packed with antioxidants that pairs really well with the menu.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
There are 12 Bento sets ($8.80) to choose from, ranging from Western, Chinese, Malay to Local and also fusion cuisines! (Swipe to see) ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Featured here are:⁣⁣⁣⁣
⭐️Bento Set G ( Japanese Set)⁣⁣⁣⁣
⭐️Bento Set K ( Western Cuisine)⁣⁣⁣⁣
⭐️Bento Set E ( Malay Cuisine)⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
The micro buffets are designed for families who enjoy eating together without the hassle of cooking especially during the Circuit Breaker period. There are 9 different sets to choose from and all priced at $38.80 nett. (Swipe to see)⁣⁣⁣ Remember to save this post so that you can refer when ordering. ⁣
⁣
⁣⁣⁣ Featured here are:⁣⁣⁣⁣
Micro Buffet Combo Set D⁣⁣⁣⁣
( Ideal for 4paxs Family meal)⁣⁣ Seaweed Egg Drop Soup⁣⁣⁣⁣
紫菜蛋花汤⁣⁣⁣⁣
Chinese Olive Fried Rice⁣⁣⁣⁣
橄榄菜炒饭⁣⁣⁣⁣
Chinese Steamed Chicken Mince with Dong Chai⁣⁣⁣⁣
冬菜蒸鸡饼⁣⁣⁣⁣
Stir Fry Cabbage with Black Fungus⁣⁣⁣⁣
⿊⽊⽿⾼丽菜⁣⁣⁣⁣
Sweet & Sour Pineapple Snapper Fillet⁣⁣⁣⁣
糖醋红鲷⻥⽚ ⁣⁣ ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Order through @villagenasilemak (you can have nasi lemak delivered in the same order too! See my previous post. ) or whatsapp Mr Ten Lee at +65 9655 9568. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Delivery islandwide on Foodpanda and Grab Food or you can email them for group orders too. ⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Thank you Michelle & Mr Ten of @noshkitchensg for delivering these delicious food to us. ⁣⁣⁣We really enjoyed the meal! ⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣
